'''丝蝽科'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|Plokiophilidae}}）又名'''蛛網蝽科'''<ref name = Zhang2010>{{ cite thesis | degree = 博士 | author = 张丹丽 | year = 2017 | title = 臭虫总科全证据系统发育研究及黑头叉胸花蝽谱系生物地理学研究 | publisher = [[南开大学|南开大学]]生命科学学院 | pages = | url = }}</ref>、'''蛛巢椿象科'''，是[[半翅目|半翅目]][[異翅亞目|異翅亞目]]{{le|臭蟲總科|Cimicomorpha}}的一[[科_(生物)|科]]，在[[熱帶|熱帶]]區域的各洲都有零星分布<ref name = Štys1967>{{cite journal | author = Štys, P. | year = 1967 | title = ''Lipokiphila chtnai'' gen. n., sp. n.—— A new genus of Plokiophilidae (Heteroptera) from Brasil | journal = ''Acta Entomologica Bohemoslovaca'' | issn = 0001-5601 | volume = 64 | pages = 248-258 | doi =  | url = http://www.digitalniknihovna.cz/knav/view/uuid:b77bd063-148b-11e1-8339-001143e3f55c?page=uuid:b77bd16f-148b-11e1-8339-001143e3f55c | access-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417182737/http://www.digitalniknihovna.cz/knav/view/uuid:b77bd063-148b-11e1-8339-001143e3f55c?page=uuid:b77bd16f-148b-11e1-8339-001143e3f55c }}</ref><ref name = Carpintero2005>{{ cite journal | author = Carpintero, D. L.; Dellapè, P. M. | year = 2005 | title = A new species and first record of ''Embiophila'' (Heteroptera: Plokiophilidae) from Nicaragua | journal = ''Studies on Neotropical Fauna and Environment'' | issn = 0165-0521 | volume = 40 | issue = 1 | pages = 65-65 | doi = 10.1080/01650520400007322 }}</ref><ref name = Schuh2015>{{cite journal | author = Schuh, R.; Štys, P.; Cassis, G.; Lenhert, M.; Swanson, D.; Bruce, T. | year = 2015 | title = New genera and species of Plokiophilidae from Australia, Fiji, and Southeast Asia, with a revised classification of the family (Insecta, Heteroptera, Cimicoidea) | journal = ''American Museum Novitates'' | issn = 0003-0082 | volume = 3825 | pages = 1-24 | doi = 10.1206/3825.1 | url = http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/handle/2246/6577?show=full | access-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417182735/http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/handle/2246/6577?show=full }}</ref>。體型極小，全長通常不超過3毫米<ref name = Luo2021>{{cite journal | last1 = Luo | first1 = J. | last2 = Peng | first2 = Y. | last3 = Xie | first3 = Q. | title = First record of the cimicomorphan family Plokiophilidae (Hemiptera, Heteroptera) from China, with description of a new species of ''Plokiophiloides'' | journal = ZooKeys | volume = 1021 | pages = 145-157 | date = 2021 | doi = 10.3897/zookeys.1021.56599 | url = https://zookeys.pensoft.net/article/56599 | access-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-04-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210421143620/https://zookeys.pensoft.net/article/56599/ }}</ref>，常寄居在[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]或[[足絲蟻|足絲蟻]]的網上，並以寄主的猎物或食物残渣为食，因而得名<ref name = China1953>{{ cite journal | author = China, W. E. | year = 1953 | title = A new subfamily of Microphysidae (Hemiptera-Heteroptera) | journal = ''Annals and Magazine of Natural History'' | series = 12 | volume = 6 | issue = 61 | pages = 61-74 | doi = 10.1080/00222935308654396 }}</ref>。

絲蝽科最初被視為{{le|駝蝽科|Microphysidae}}的一個亞科<ref name = China1953/>，但絲蝽與駝蝽在[[口器|口器]]構造<!---{{le|下唇 (昆蟲)|Insect mouthparts#Labium|下唇}}各節的長度比例上有所不同--->、後翅翅脈分布、[[產卵管|產卵管]]長度和[[授精|授精]]方式等方面都有所不同，且駝蝽科更接近{{le|盲椿總科|Miroidea}}，而非原先所認為的臭蟲總科成員。鑑於這些差異，絲蝽從駝蝽科分出，成為一個獨立的科<ref name = Carayon1961/><ref name = Štys1967/>，至今包含三個亞科與不到十個屬<ref name = Luo2021/>。

